<br>
Americans don’t usually refer to Los Angeles, they say “LA”.  If you are trying to tell your friend over the phone how to get to this board, you don’t say “Well, the universal resource locator field is…”<br>
<br>
Presumably it would be the same in Norrath.<br>
<br>
It’s much easier to imagine a burly warrior in a dungeon screaming out “Mez the BTG!  Mez it!”  Instead of “Mesmerize the blood-thirsty ghoul!  Mesmerize it!”, which would be quickly followed by “Argh!  My spleen!”<br>
<br>
So for me, someone asking, “Could I have you cast spirit of the wolf on me, please?” would be much the same as me asking, “When we go to the store, should we take the sport utility vehicle or the miniature van?”<br>
